title: Howard Stern Sternthology (Whole Lotta Ronnie Week) Part 2
description:
Howard Stern Sternthology (Whole Lotta Ronnie Week) Part 2  (02:34:18)


* Ronnie On Wrap Up – Howard plays clips from The Wrap Up Show of his limo driver claiming that Baba Booey has it in for him (3/30/2011)

* Sternac – A deep cut featuring Howard as the all-knowing soothsayer, Sternac (4/13/1987)

* NASCAR Ronnie – “Whole Lotta Ronnie” continues with a caller challenging Ronnie on his NASCAR knowledge (6/17/2015)

* Victoria Jackson – Former SNL star opens up about being a “Not Ready For Primetime Player” in the 80’s and discusses her right-wing political & religious beliefs (10/16/2012)

* Tan Mom Oswego Trip – Howard and Sal discuss and play clips from a wild weekend appearance in Oswego, NY with Tan Mom (6/13/2016)

* Call Of Duty Release – Correspondent Wolfie talks to video game geeks as they wait in line for the new “Call Of Duty” game (11/28/2012)
